I think the chairman
was inspired by The Godfather,

00:20:15.527 --> 00:20:17.446
because he suddenly set up family lunches.

00:20:18.363 --> 00:20:19.364
- "Family lunches"?
- "Family lunches"?

00:20:19.448 --> 00:20:20.282
Yeah.

